25:14.697 --> 25:17.940
Both of those gentlemen had just been a

25:19.118 --> 25:22.043
Really a great effort for me.

25:22.584 --> 25:23.826
Tremendous help.

25:25.328 --> 25:25.809
Let's see.

25:26.470 --> 25:28.454
Who succeeded Dave Maxwell as dean?

25:35.666 --> 25:36.087
Jones?

25:37.870 --> 25:38.751
I don't know.

25:38.871 --> 25:39.933
See, I was gone by then.

25:39.953 --> 25:42.337
I think I was gone, too.

25:42.357 --> 25:44.080
I don't know where.

25:45.460 --> 25:46.141
Oh, no.

25:46.161 --> 25:46.281
What?

25:46.301 --> 25:46.741
